sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Look Graph Webview
participant Router as GraphMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as CreateWorktreeUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements RepositoryOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: New worktree from branch
App->>Router: graph/createWorktree(repositoryLocator, branch, path, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, branch, path, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: addWorktree({ branch, path }, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: addWorktree(executionContext, { branch, path }, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: addWorktree(executionContext, { branch, path }, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: success
Runtime-->>Repo: success
Repo-->>UseCase: success
UseCase->>Registry: discoverWorktrees(Repo)
Registry-->>UseCase: updated WorktreeLocator list
UseCase-->>Router: updated WorktreeLocator list
Router-->>App: graph/createWorktreeResponse(requestId, worktrees)
Router-->>App: graph/refreshRequested
App-->>User: Show new worktree annotation
